{"tid":2161112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自從上次血債票償單野 已經想屌泛民好耐","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T06:14:03.000Z","uid":271497,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be323a1e2d040c0406f77e28df7a81774e1483bd","tid":2161112,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"講真反送中之前不嬲無理泛民做過啲乜，但係真心頂唔順依兩年嚟泛民永遠都係關鍵時候食人血同賣手足。<br />\n到咗今時今日泛民究竟仲有咩藉口留係非法臨會做花瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都出哂聲叫泛民總辭，杯葛非法臨會，泛民仲夠膽死放風想繼續留係非法臨會做花瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔敢代表其他人，但係我自己既睇法係:<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">依單野邊個選擇做二五仔，企係中共個邊反插我地一刀嘅，一律當共狗狙佢老母臭閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n預咗比人屌五毛分化撚，有唔同意見嘅不妨除咗負皮之外，一齊討論吓。"},{"pid":"4aabb2f784f2d6c63605bdbdd0ff1faf7b463ab5","tid":2161112,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"youtuber Auman好快就開審<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"036cab5b367444a0f9f9c8b194c242b06d814d75","tid":2161112,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e698135b5550c03ae6c192e61e45365d5b9a952","tid":2161112,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036cab5b367444a0f9f9c8b194c242b06d814d75","tid":2161112,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"竟然有人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2025dce308d2c6f4fdc5e2bfd2a83dc62e927325","tid":2161112,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"pussh"},{"pid":"07e7e371fe1e1919a016dadc37ad5eaf42233a89","tid":2161112,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e698135